The paper deals with image caption generation and optical character recognition, which are both sub-fields of computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper uses deep learning-based systems, which are often studied in the sub-fields of natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
